{"tid":1145440,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"嘗試語譯泰國人有冇問題","createTime":"2019-05-08T17:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T16:38:14.000Z","uid":111088,"like":3,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"03f67dbfbce0c8dc94dd6987487db6932b859dc4","tid":1145440,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"原片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S7sq-ivmD2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS7sq-ivmD2o&d=fyMqA0bs77BZF9qEbHCyfsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=a898ed88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S7sq-ivmD2o</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國人語譯：<br />\n你有咩問題=咩料呀你/是咪short撚左<br />\n一個人，你同我=屌你出嚟隻揪啦<br />\n一個鐘，42=屌我等你架42號等左成個鐘<br />\n泰國想講：<br />\n屌你係咪傻撚左呀？我等你架42號等撚左我成粒鐘喎，而家點撚樣先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你咁串，出嚟隻揪吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好恰鳩我泰國人呀，我唔卸你呀我話你知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係咪男人嚟嫁，咁冇承擔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落車吖我同你講清楚條數點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc07aeb8215d0cd6d6e3bf6e5a5465593f9afabd","tid":1145440,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:20:25.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"bdc842088af35547ba85b5841bc5ebcba1cd95e0","tid":1145440,"uid":249885,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時開show"},{"pid":"dcbb34facf6bab21115b0f349e48c3513ec916c5","tid":1145440,"uid":69289,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T18:05:21.000Z","msg":"，"},{"pid":"1e711edc726cca5c0371d9b38c7afc26b38d8d86","tid":1145440,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T18:41:57.000Z","msg":"估吓佢講咩姐"},{"pid":"be763fe94f052f00626ed8f